com.hcl.domino.data

Interface IDTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<Integer>, IAdaptable, Iterable<Integer>, Set<Integer>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DocumentSelection

    public interface IDTable
extends IAdaptable, Set<Integer>
    Wraps the C API IDTable, a very efficient set of note ids that is sorted in ascending order

    • Field Summary

      static long NOTEID_FLAG_DELETED
